item_prototype.description:
Monitors Microsoft SQL Server Agent service state.

Windows service status returned values:
0 - service running;
1 - service paused;
2 - service starting (start pending);
3 - service pausing (pause pending);
4 - service starting after pause (continue pending);
5 - service stopping (stop pending);
6 - service stopped;
7 - service state unknown;
255 - unable to get current service state.

